      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of August 11 Business Day article on plan by Lucent Technologies to spin off its enterprise networks group as separate company</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A report in the Company News column of Business Day on Friday about a plan by Lucent Technologies to spin off its enterprise networks group as a separate company to be called Avaya misstated the size of the unit's work force. It is 34,000 employees, not 7,000.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>A report in the Company News column of Business Day on Friday about a plan by Lucent Technologies to spin off its enterprise networks group as a separate company to be called Avaya misstated the size of the unit's work force. It is 34,000 employees, not 7,000.</p>
      </block>
